<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٣٩:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: <span class="c3">{إِنَّ إِبْرَاهِيمَ لَأَوَّاهٌ حَلِيمٌ}</span> <span class="c4">[التوبة: ١١٤]</span>،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ أَبُو مَيْسَرَةَ:</span> الرَّحِيمُ بِلِسَانِ الحَبَشَةِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٦٣:</span> <span class="c3">{لَأَوَّاهٌ}</span>: " شَفَقًا، وَفَرَقًا،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ الشَّاعِرُ:</span> <span class="c4">[البحر الوافر]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>إِذَا قُمْتُ أَرْحَلُهَا بِلَيْلٍ ... تَأَوَّهُ آهَةَ الرَّجُلِ الحَزِينِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>